<page xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      navpath="events,symposium">
  <title>2015 Ontology Summit Symposium</title>
  
  <content>
    <p>
    Following its established pattern, this year's <strong><a
    href="http://ontolog.cim3.net/OntologySummit/">Ontology
    Summit</a></strong> consists of a series of <a
    href="virtuals.html">weekly virtual discussions</a>, followed by a
    2-day face-to-face symposium.
    </p>

    <h3>Schedule</h3>
    <p>This year's face-to-face symposium will be <strong>April 13 and
    14</strong>.  Several excellent keynote speakers, expert panels,
    and group discussions are on the docket for this year.<a
    href="schedule.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm pull-right">See
    the Schedule...</a></p>

    <h3>Venue</h3>
    <p>We will again be graciously hosted by <a
    href="https://www.nitrd.gov/">NITRD</a> at the <a
    href="http://www.nsf.gov/">NSF</a> in <strong>Arlington, Virginia,
    USA</strong>:
    <ul>
      <li>NSF Boardroom (room 1235)<br/>
      Stafford Place I<br/>
      4201 Wilson Boulevard<br/>
      Arlington, VA 22230, USA
      </li>
    </ul>
    </p>
    
    <p>A map of the site and directions from the nearby Ballston-MU
    Metro station are available <a
    href="https://www.nitrd.gov/nitrdgroups/images/9/9b/Directions_Map_to_NSF_Room_I-1235.pdf">here</a>.
    </p>

    <h3>Registration</h3>
    <p>The symposium is free of charge, but all physical attendees
    must <a href="registration.html">register</a> in advance.  <a
    href="registration.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm
    pull-right">Register!</a></p>

  </content>
</page>

